videos.headline: Mitchell breaks free for 44-yard Louisiana TD
videos.description: Elijah Mitchell takes a quick handoff and finds an opening to the end zone for a 44-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Louisiana's Trahan takes off for 53-yard pick-six
